MatrixSub - class MatrixSub.
Matrix substitution used for alignment : transition/transversion matrix for Nucleic Acid ; identity matrix or Blosum50 matrix for Amino-Acids.
MatrixSub() - Constructor for class MatrixSub
Default constructor (matrix table is identity matrix for Nucleic Acids)
MatrixSub(int) - Constructor for class MatrixSub
Indicative Constructor : 0 for identity matrix nucleic acid ; 1 for transition-transversion matrix nucleic acid ; 2 for blast matrix nucleic acid ; 5 for identity matrix for amino-acids ; 6 for blosum50 matrix for amino-acids ; 7 for pam250 matrix for amino-acids ; ...
